03:07.865 --> 03:08.966
What?

03:09.033 --> 03:11.068
Amy, think about it. We can't do
this. We can't do this to John.

03:11.135 --> 03:14.105
There are a lot of bad
consequences to lying

03:14.171 --> 03:16.874
