okay to lie could be one of them.

03:16.941 --> 03:19.143
Telling the truth can have bad
consequences, too, you know.

03:19.210 --> 03:22.113
Come on, let's just get everything
out in the open and deal with it.

03:22.179 --> 03:24.048
